<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Urgent: Complete Form 433a</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>This step is not optional. If we don’t complete the 433a together,
            we can’t take the right actions with the IRS, we can’t request
            relief, and we can’t resolve your case.</p>
          <p>We understand this part can feel personal. Sharing your finances
            isn’t easy, and it can seem overwhelming. But you're not expected to
            do it alone. We'll walk through it with you, step by step, live on
            the phone. If you're missing something or unsure where to find it,
            we’ll help you figure it out.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">But you have to make
            the call.</p>
          <p>We’re ready to do the work, but without your input, we can’t move
            forward. There’s no way around this step, and the longer it’s
            delayed, the harder it becomes to protect your case.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call us now at
            <a
              href="tel:{{phone}}"
              style="color: #d9534f; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{phone}}</a>. Let’s get this done together.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;"> {{{signature}}}</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

  </body>
</html>